    <div class="speak-how"><strong>How:</strong> One recording, timer on. <strong>When you listen back, check:</strong> <em>AT seven, IN the morning, ON Mondays.</em></div>
  </div>

  <div class="tip-box">
    <h3>Tips: talk about your day every day</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Say your morning aloud while you live it: <em>"Now I'm making coffee&hellip;"</em> One minute a day is real practice.</li>
      <li>Learn routines as pairs: <em>wake up / get up, go to work / come home.</em></li>
      <li>The word <em>usually</em> sounds like <em>"YOO-zhuh-lee"</em> &mdash; three beats. Say it five times!</li>
