  <h2 class="sec-title"><span class="tab-num">4</span>Vocabulary: Hobbies &amp; Free Time</h2>

  <h3 style="color:var(--plum);">4.1 — Hobbies &amp; Activities</h3>
  <div class="vocab-grid">
    <div class="vocab-card"><span class="emoji">🎨</span><div><b>painting</b>making pictures with paint</div></div>
    <div class="vocab-card"><span class="emoji">🎸</span><div><b>playing the guitar</b>making music with a guitar</div></div>
    <div class="vocab-card"><span class="emoji">🌱</span><div><b>gardening</b>growing plants and flowers</div></div>
