      <div class="bubble left"><div class="name">Pablo</div>Come over tonight! I'll cook. Let me check what I have... I have <span class="highlight">some</span> rice and <span class="highlight">some</span> eggs, but I don't have <span class="highlight">any</span> vegetables.</div>
